{
  "DPPPPXW-1A": "Basic instinct. Rule number one: as far from the door as possible. You don't want someone to hit you with the door handle right at the entrance, or be the welcoming committee for every newcomer.",
  "WXPPPPD-1B": "Mirror basic. Same as 1A, just from the other side. The wall is your shield, the door is the threat.",
  
  "DXPPPOW-2A": "Tactical retreat. That first guy smartly took the wall spot. You have no choice but to go straight to the door. As far from him as possible - no inspection of other people's equipment today.",
