  "WPOXPOD-3D": "Group breaker. They let you in the middle? Take it. Break their weird formation and establish order.",
  
  "DOPXOOW-4A": "Buffer zone. Two guys on the right and one at the door. You get the spot between them. Tight, but at least you have one side covered by an empty space.",
